text: Zdeněk Bárta (15 May 1891 - 1 April 1987) was a Bohemian fencer. He competed in the individual épée and sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1987 deaths Category:People from Ledeč nad Sázavou Category:People from the Kingdom of Bohemia Category:Czech male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Bohemia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
